title: Cafe Wesa'e
description: A 100% vegetarian/vegan restaurant using whole local foods with a slow food concept. Gluten free available. Menu items are soup, entrees, salads, raw desserts and sweet treats, made-in-house coffee and more. All food is prepared from scratch every day. Serves breakfast and lunch only. Small private space. Relaxed communal style seating. Air-conditioning. Ample parking. Yoga/Pilates/Ballet studio upstairs. Located opposite Toyota/Leader.
streetAddress: Rua Comoro, Delta II, Comoro, Timor Leste
